      </li>
      
      <li class="ctsh clearfix" data-cid="18395926">
        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/qiuyansun/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u4243534-3.jpg" alt="sunson" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/18395926/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/18395926/" class="">第3页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/qiuyansun/" class=" " title="sunson">sunson</a>
              
                <span class="allstar40" title="推荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="18395926">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">权不重，故不敢以兵威劫远人；望不隆，故不敢以诛夷待勋旧；学不夙，故不敢以智慧轻儒素；恩不洽，故不敢以苛法督吏民。

英之光荣革命或与之有类似之处。
“以兵威劫远人；以诛夷待勋旧；以智慧轻儒素；以苛法督吏民；”呵呵，贵国。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2012-05-19 23:08</span>
                  
                    &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="">1人喜欢</span>
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <blockquote><q>权不重，故不敢以兵威劫远人；望不隆，故不敢以诛夷待勋旧；学不夙，故不敢以智慧轻儒素；恩不洽，故不敢以苛法督吏民。</q></blockquote><div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>英之光荣革命或与之有类似之处。<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>“以兵威劫远人；以诛夷待勋旧；以智慧轻儒素；以苛法督吏民；”呵呵，贵国。
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







